  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Nuckelavee is an abstract, indie horror game based on Scottish folklore, history and the Gaelic language. You must find ancient artifacts scattered across a procedurally generated island and remove the curse placed upon them.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259240/extras/81532c45c75313116341d30886c35841.avif?t=1765895790\" width=720 height=64 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259240/extras/f199700dc8033b807cbcda73c76c9a8d.poster.avif?t=1765895790\" width=720 height=404 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259240/extras/f199700dc8033b807cbcda73c76c9a8d.webm?t=1765895790\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259240/extras/f199700dc8033b807cbcda73c76c9a8d.mp4?t=1765895790\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Explore the island, find books, notes, music and artifacts left behind, they may help you in your task or tell you a story.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259240/extras/56458597af36a4cdc00d71c1c5c671d6.avif?t=1765895790\" width=720 height=64 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259240/extras/fb4c4037ff22d58b6c537f70f82baca8.poster.avif?t=1765895790\" width=720 height=404 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259240/extras/fb4c4037ff22d58b6c537f70f82baca8.webm?t=1765895790\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259240/extras/fb4c4037ff22d58b6c537f70f82baca8.mp4?t=1765895790\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Solve the puzzle that locks in the curse. Do not allow them to be tainted again!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259240/extras/0f4bcfe4cb4bed5995fd3bb5c396e63e.avif?t=1765895790\" width=720 height=64 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259240/extras/0a0df250a7c3a56378fd79b6362947d2.poster.avif?t=1765895790\" width=720 height=404 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259240/extras/0a0df250a7c3a56378fd79b6362947d2.webm?t=1765895790\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259240/extras/0a0df250a7c3a56378fd79b6362947d2.mp4?t=1765895790\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Evade! You may not have many weapons in your arsenal. Avoid Nuckelavee at all costs!<br></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The game does not currently support saving progress, it is intended to be played as each play is a new run. This may change as player feedback indicate they want it. </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Nuckelavee is an abstract, indie horror game based on Scottish folklore, history and the Gaelic language. You must find ancient artifacts scattered across a procedurally generated island and remove the curse placed upon them.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259240/extras/81532c45c75313116341d30886c35841.avif?t=1765895790\" width=720 height=64 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259240/extras/f199700dc8033b807cbcda73c76c9a8d.poster.avif?t=1765895790\" width=720 height=404 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259240/extras/f199700dc8033b807cbcda73c76c9a8d.webm?t=1765895790\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259240/extras/f199700dc8033b807cbcda73c76c9a8d.mp4?t=1765895790\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Explore the island, find books, notes, music and artifacts left behind, they may help you in your task or tell you a story.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259240/extras/56458597af36a4cdc00d71c1c5c671d6.avif?t=1765895790\" width=720 height=64 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259240/extras/fb4c4037ff22d58b6c537f70f82baca8.poster.avif?t=1765895790\" width=720 height=404 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259240/extras/fb4c4037ff22d58b6c537f70f82baca8.webm?t=1765895790\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259240/extras/fb4c4037ff22d58b6c537f70f82baca8.mp4?t=1765895790\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Solve the puzzle that locks in the curse. Do not allow them to be tainted again!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259240/extras/0f4bcfe4cb4bed5995fd3bb5c396e63e.avif?t=1765895790\" width=720 height=64 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259240/extras/0a0df250a7c3a56378fd79b6362947d2.poster.avif?t=1765895790\" width=720 height=404 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259240/extras/0a0df250a7c3a56378fd79b6362947d2.webm?t=1765895790\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259240/extras/0a0df250a7c3a56378fd79b6362947d2.mp4?t=1765895790\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Evade! You may not have many weapons in your arsenal. Avoid Nuckelavee at all costs!<br></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The game does not currently support saving progress, it is intended to be played as each play is a new run. This may change as player feedback indicate they want it. </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
